posts.title: Today is a sad day for me.  No joy.
posts.content:
My family has been torn apart again by my TDS suffering parents.

There isn't going to be a reconciliation after this one.

I was storing my boat at my parents place. When I dropped it off there were huge Kamala signs in her yard last week. Today I went to get the boat after our falling out to store it at my FIL's farm. Our falling out was the day after I dropped my boat off. Today six days later there isn't a campaign sign in their yard. I laughed my ass off. All she had to do was keep politics out of family but noooooooo. Had to go after my wife for her views and tried to humiliate and shame her online. When my wife asked if she really wanted to go there and she did. So my wife put her in her place.

Then they tell my brother to call me to tell me to put my wife in her place. Basically I not so nicely told them all to fuck off. Then my brother tries to reconcile when he realizes it was his mother being the cunt and not my wife. Too late fuckers.

I really tried to have a relationship with them but they have gotten so many COVID boosters I think it made them retarded. I can't family with them anymore.

I know this belongs on Reddit.

But I did chuckle that they at least realized maybe it is them that looks like crazy fools and took down the signs. My mom tried to gaslight my wife and say she wasn't directing it at her........but she was. Fucking Democrats really think people are stupid.

At least the holidays will be peaceful and quiet. And I wont have to travel. That's a bonus. Maybe I'll smoke a brisket with the gas money I save.
